gobblin.restli

Class EmbeddedRestliServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractIdleService
      • gobblin.restli.EmbeddedRestliServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Service

    public class EmbeddedRestliServer
extends AbstractIdleService
    An embedded Rest.li server using Netty. Usage: EmbeddedRestliServer server = EmbeddedRestliServer.builder().resources(List).build(); server.startAsync() The server is a Service that provides access to a collection of Rest.li resources. The following are optional settings (available through builder pattern): * port - defaults to randomly chosen port between MIN_PORT and MAX_PORT. * log - defaults to class Logger. * name - defaults to the name of the first resource in the resource collection. * injector - an Injector to inject dependencies into the Rest.li resources.
